      <title>被控策划谋杀总督的前菲律宾国会议员在东帝汶被捕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-22/former-filipino-congressman-accused-of-masterminding-a-governor-s-murder-is-arrested-in-east-timor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾马尼拉（美联社）——菲律宾司法官员周五表示，一名被指控策划杀害一名省长和其他几人的前菲律宾国会议员已在东帝汶被捕，并将被驱逐到菲律宾。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-22/former-filipino-congressman-accused-of-masterminding-a-governor-s-murder-is-arrested-in-east-timor</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 07:50:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
